title: News & "Go Get My Lunch" 2014 season edition
itunes:title: News & "Go Get My Lunch" 2014 season edition
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- recap the latest NFL news including the Ray Rice situation and injury news around the league. Then, the trio play the first "Go Get My Lunch" round of the 2014 NFL season, revealing bold predictions involving Matt Ryan, Calvin Johnson and much more.
